<p>Dr. Manoj K Johar brings extensive experience in plastic and reconstructive surgery, with specialized expertise in <a href="/scars/">scar management</a>. His approach combines technical precision with an artistic eye for aesthetics, ensuring that each patient receives personalized care designed to achieve natural-looking results. Whether you have a minor scar that needs improvement or a more complex scarring condition, Dr. Johar can develop a customized treatment plan to help you achieve smoother, more confident skin.</p>

